{"id": "1476233048503750778", "channel_id": "1476233048503750778", "type": 0, "author_id": "1474226197272727613", "author_name": "liukankam", "author_bot": false, "content": "1.感觉主线敌人的伤害与血量膨胀太快了,一开始才30几伤害后面五六章几百,而且首领血量越来越血牛,可同时期唤醒体伤害护盾提升很小像蚊子腿.\n2.em,我是新手才入坑十天,感觉游戏沒有攻略之类的,而平台上攻略过于碎片化,如果游戏内可以知道选什么命轮和命契就好了.\n1. The damage and health of main enemies seem to increase too quickly. Initially, they only deal around 30 damage, but by chapters five and six, it's hundreds. Bosses also become increasingly tanky, while the damage and shield increases from awakened forms are negligible.\n\n2. I'm a newbie, only been playing for ten days. It feels like there aren't any guides or anything like that, and the guides on the platform are too fragmented. It would be great if the game provided information on which Destiny Wheels and Destiny Contracts to choose within the game itself.", "timestamp": "2026-02-25T15:03:05.847000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-02-25T15:09:55.311000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1476233048503750778", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」意见反馈", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
